      <title>Arunachal Photo Diary</title>
      <link>https://aparajith21.github.io/post/arunachal-photo-diary/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://aparajith21.github.io/post/arunachal-photo-diary/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;We started from Chennai on the 22nd of December, flying to Dibrugarh via Kolkata. We reached Dibrugarh at 2 p.m. and were anxious to get out of that place due to the ensuing protests against the CAA. We entered Arunachal at around 4 and reached the Golden Pagoda at Namsai at around 1730 in the evening.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://aparajith21.github.io/post/2020-02-16-arunachal-photo-diary/map.png&#34; alt=&#34;Map of Arunachal Pradesh&#34;&gt;
Route Taken: Namsai (Namsai District) (Day 1) -&amp;gt; Hawai (Anjaw District) (Day 2) -&amp;gt; Dong (Day 3) -&amp;gt; Kibithu (Day 4) -&amp;gt; Tezu (Lohit District) (Day 5) -&amp;gt; Roing (Lower Dibang Valley District) (Day 6) -&amp;gt; Pasighat (East Siang District) (Day 6)-&amp;gt; Dibrugarh (Day 8) -&amp;gt; Chennai&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://aparajith21.github.io/post/2020-02-16-arunachal-photo-diary/IMG_20200115_133044.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Golden Pagoda, Namsai&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figcaption&gt;Golden Pagoda, Namsai&lt;/figcaption&gt;
