&lt;figcaption&gt;Monastery by the Tengapani River&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://aparajith21.github.io/post/2020-02-16-arunachal-photo-diary/parashuram_kund.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Parashuram Kund by the Lohit River&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figcaption&gt;Parashuram Kund by Lohit River&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://aparajith21.github.io/post/2020-02-16-arunachal-photo-diary/BRO.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Interesting from the BRO&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figcaption&gt;Interesting board from the BRO&lt;/figcaption&gt;
Other more interesting boards on the road by the BRO include:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If you drive like hell, soon you will be there&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Better be Mr Late than late Mr&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Safety on the road is safe tea at home&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;After whiskey, driving risky&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your hurry may cause your family worry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This is not a race, drive with grace&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep your nerves on sharp curves; &amp;amp; many others&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://aparajith21.github.io/post/2020-02-16-arunachal-photo-diary/lohit_dong.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Lohit River at Dong&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
